All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Board
The Board class represents the game board in the Pipe Mania game, COntains pipelines and logic related to board management
Main
The 'main' class represents the main interface of the Pipe Mania game.
NodeST
The NodeST class represents a node used in the binary search tree data structure which is used in the game's score table.
PipeLine
The PipeLine class represents a pipe in the game Pipe Mania.
PipeLineType
The PipeLineType enumeration represents the different types of pipes available in the Pipe Mania Game.
PipeManiaSystem
The PipeManiaSystem class represents the main system of the Pipe Mania Game.
Player
The Player class represents a player in a game with a nickname. and a score.
ScoreTable
The ScoreTable class represents a score table for players.
